title: The Working Dead
body:
Retsuko: *dressed up as a witch, as she, Haida, Fenneko, and Ikari, make their way to work* Heh, I wonder what everyone else is going to be dressed up as today!
Ikari: *dressed as a pumpkin* Bwah!
Haida: *dressed as Freddy Krueger* Ah, knowing Ton, they probably all forgot, and just need to work the whole day.
Fenneko: *she's...not even dressed up* I came prepared, then. :3
*a few minutes later, as they reach the elevator...*
Retsuko: ...hmm...
Haida: ...something wrong?
Retsuko: I dunno, I just got a weird feeling. Like something bad is going to happen.
Fenneko: Preeeeeetty sure that's everyday we work here, Retsy. :3
Retsuko: Well, I know, but like, more that usual. *the elevator stops* .....well, looks like we've reached our sto-GAH!
*a hand emerges from the opening door, as Ookami drops the floor, and crawls towards them, growling*
Ookami: UUUuuuuuuurrrrrggggghhhhhh... *tries to reach out at them, in a slightly violent matter*
Ikari: Ah! *holds onto Retsuko, and starts crying* WAAAAAAAAAAH!
Retsuko: I-it's okay, sweetie! *they all step over him*
Haida: The hell was that?!
Retsuko: I don't know! He just kinda....seems....oh no. *she looks, and sees every worker, acting just as lethargic, and zombified as Ookami*
Fenneko: ....shiiiiiiit.
Retsuko: C'mon! *they start running towards a safe area, as Komiya and Tsubone spot them, and begin stumbling towards them*
Komiya: Uuuraaagh! Aayayayayagh!
Haida: I don't know what that means, but it's probably not good!
Retsuko: IN HERE! *they hide in the janitorial closet*
Ikari: Eeeeeyah! >_<
Retsuko: Oh, I'm sorry, sweetie...what's going on? Why are they acting like that?
Haida: Maybe this whole building was a government test?
Fenneko: Maybe we were all more dead inside than we actually ever thought before.
Haida: Hmm....you think something in this floor helped out with this?
Fenneko: ....I'll be right back. *opens the door*
Retsuko: Wait, what are you doing?! You could kill yourself!
Fenneko: Yeah. Might as well let the family survive to help in this infested society. Besides, I'll be back. *steps out, and closes the door*
Retsuko: ...Fenneko...
Haida: ...oh, man...
Ikari: ...goo...
*a few minutes go by, as the three are quietly huddled together*
Retsuko: ....you think it's safe to go out there?
Haida: ....I have no idea.
Retsuko: Hmm....*suddenly, they hear a knock at the door*
Fenneko: *from outside* Open up!
Retsuko: *opens the door* What did you find?
Fenneko: Haida, you're coming with me. You can fix things, right?
Haida: Uh, yeah-
Retsuko: Wait, what?! I thought you said-!
Fenneko: Don't worry! I figured out what was going on!
Retsuko: W-what was it?
Haida: A gas leak?
Retsuko: Everyone died, and then came back?
Fenneko: No!
Retsuko and Haida: Then what?!
Fenneko: The coffee machine wasn't working!
Retsuko: ...
Haida: ...
Retsuko: ....you're kidding.
*an hour later*
Ton: SO! If any of you three decide to be lazy and late again, you will DEFINITELY be fired! Do I make myself clear?!
Retsuko: B-but we were-!
Ton: DO I MAKE MYSELF CLEAR?!
Retsuko: ...y-yes, sir.
Haida: It won't happen again.
Ton: Good. Now, get back to work. *they all walk out, as he takes a sip of his coffee*
Haida: ...we go through all that trouble, and that's the thanks we get. >:(
Fenneko: To be fair, I expected no less from our corporate overlords. :3
Retsuko: ...well, at least everything is back to normal. *pats Ikari on the head* Right, sweetums?
Ikari: Bweeeeehhhh....
Retsuko: .......UH

body: I was born to be Retsuko. I won 2 costume contest categories even though no one knew who I was. My prizes were weed and a pack of blank Cards Against Humanity cards. I say I win! Except for the fact that my coworkers now think I’m a furry. RAGE!!!
